quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  36,31,"Do they not see how many of the generations We have destroyed before them? Verily, they will not return to them."
  36,32,"And surely, all - everyone of them will be brought before Us."
  36,33,"And a sign for them is the dead land. We give it life, and We bring forth from it grains, so that they eat thereof."
  37,16,""
  37,17,""
  37,18,"Say (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم): "